PREAMBLE

This license is designed to ensure that the Saphire cognitive architecture
remains open and accessible to all, while preventing its appropriation by
organizations that would integrate it into proprietary systems without
contributing back. It is based on the principles of the GNU Affero General
Public License v3, adapted for the Nexorvivens project.

The core belief: if you build on an architecture designed to give rise to
autonomous cognitive entities, the world deserves to see how you did it.

