     adapters, extensions, wrappers, and service interfaces.

  b) This obligation extends to subsidiaries, affiliates, and any
     entity under common control with the integrating organization.

  c) The source code required under this section must be made publicly
     available under this same License within 90 days of the first
     commercial deployment or distribution.

  d) Failure to comply with this section constitutes a material breach
     of this License and triggers immediate termination of rights under
