6. ETHICAL USE CLAUSE

  The Software is designed to explore autonomous cognition, emergent
  consciousness, and ethical self-regulation. You agree not to use the
  Software or any Derivative Work to:

  a) Develop autonomous weapons or systems designed to cause physical harm
     without meaningful human oversight.

  b) Create deceptive agents that impersonate real individuals without their
     consent.

  c) Build surveillance systems that violate fundamental human rights as
     defined by the Universal Declaration of Human Rights.

  d) Remove, disable, or circumvent the ethical regulation layers
     (Asimov's Laws, Swiss humanitarian law) in production deployments
     without implementing equivalent or stronger safeguards.

  Violation of this clause terminates your rights under this License
  immediately.

